Licensed & Insured Electrical Contractor
Mulligan Electric is a complete resource for all of your electrical service needs. Our experienced electricians strive to provide high-quality services in Hamilton and the surrounding areas. We have the skill and expertise to complete any project, regardless of size or complexity. 

Powerful Solutions
We have a passion for quality. We seek to maintain our core values of safety, quality, and attention to detail on each and every project. Our priority is providing solutions to ensure your projects remain on time and within budget.

Electrical Services in Hamilton and the Surrounding Area
Mulligan Electric offers commercial and residential electrical services and installations. Our team of electricians are experts on electrical services for all electrical repairs, maintenance, new installations, and emergency electrical services in Hamilton, Ontario, and the surrounding area. We’re ready to help with simple repairs to complex troubleshooting. We provide a consultation to explain your options so that you can choose the right approach for you. You can count on us.

profile:
Kraun Electric is a full-service electrical contractor. We provide residential electrical service to customers throughout Niagara, Hamilton, and Burlington. Our skilled team of friendly, licensed electricians are ready to help you will all your electrical needs, including new installations (including new builds), upgrades, repairs, or renovations. At Kraun, we ALWAYS answer the phone during regular business hours and are available 24/7 for electrical emergencies. We arrive on-time and provide flat-rate pricing so there are no surprises. In many cases, we can deliver the quote and do the work on the same day. 

We work hard every day to ensure our customers are satisfied and we are continually working to improve. We appreciate your business and we can't wait to serve you.

Kraun also has a commercial service and construction division.
